### Example 03 — materialize CQN aggregate

### Seeded orders (source)
GET http://localhost:4103/odata/v4/sales/Orders?$top=5

### Aggregate targets (possibly empty)
GET http://localhost:4103/odata/v4/reporting/DailyCustomerRevenue?$top=5
GET http://localhost:4103/odata/v4/reporting/RecentCustomerRevenue?$top=5

### Both pipelines should be registered
GET http://localhost:4103/pipeline/Pipelines?$select=name,mode,status
